{"tid":1061290,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"DC9硬闖車龍　逆線轉彎趕接單？","createTime":"2019-03-14T09:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T14:10:17.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"693d08544ecd3f969531a38c13cf9898bcbb581b","tid":1061290,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"明知故犯？的士硬闖車龍 逆線轉彎趕接單？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JbdoRW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JbdoRW&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=961a5e42\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JbdoRW</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190314/photo/bkn-20190314172748443-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190314175114\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190314%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190314172748443-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190314175114&h=90d93206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明知故犯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大地任我行？近日金鐘有的士逆線行駛，更穿過車龍轉彎駛離，嚇窒其他司機！<br />\n<br />\n網友Kan Lau在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」上載影片，周三（13日）晚上11時許，一輛未載客的士逆線駛出夏慤道和紅棉路交界的十字路口，當時不斷有車輛迎面而至，有司機嚇至慌忙切線閃避，現場響按聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n惟的士一於少理，待直駛的車龍經過後，繼續轉入紅棉路離去。<br />\n<br />\n有網友嘲諷的士司機：「大地任我行之神級的士BB」，有人更怒斥：「咁X仆X」。"},{"pid":"a34ba0a7c3f113f2616e6085fcdf796f5269b73e","tid":1061290,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"小巴狗的士狗廢老司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bac34ddc4c31be723bc24f5a7ea8fc787b4d180","tid":1061290,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"衝多幾次無機會衝架啦"}]}